Security Pacific National Bank, a unitof Security Pacific Corp, said the Securities and ExchangeCommission declared effective its shelf registration statementcovering 1.2 billion dlrs of mortgage related securities.    The bank said it filed the registration statement in April.This is the bank's second shelf registration filed inconnection with Security Pacific Merchant Bank's efforts tosecuritize mortgages originated by Security Pacific National,it said. Reuter&#3;